<h2 id="svm-decision-boundary">SVM Decision Boundary</h2>

<p>Minimise cost function –&gt; LHS = 0 –&gt; thetax ≥ 1 –&gt; Sub in –&gt; P must be large –&gt; margin will be far away</p>

